      "comment": "BRUNSWICK HIGH (1) is a Bruce Timbs-trained newcomer by Aussie Infrared out of Tauwitchere. Drawn favourably and can capitalise. Profiles strongly for this and can make an immediate impact. SATISFIED (3) flew the lids from out wide with a sensational early split but ran over at the finish when a narrow fourth (22.38) over 381m at Cannington. Has good early burn and is drawn to be prominent. Better than last start and can bounce back. ALL THAT GLITTER (4) has her first outing without a trial but profiles nicely for this. Among the leading players. MISS PRECOCIOUS (7) has top-three claims while fresh from a 12 weeks break.",
